ally had a good time with my camera this Parade. I even exceeded my 300MB monthly upload limit at Flickr that I had to hijack on a new account to fit all these shots in!\r\n\r\nThat''s all for now. Hope you have a Merry Christmas! ~Chad\r\n\r\n*This imagery was inspired by an episode of Pokemon, Bulbasaur-Charmander-Squirtle(-Pikachu!) era. Brock was making rice cakes when Ash noticed a camera lens (wanting to take a picture of Pikachu) appear from behind some bushes. He over-reacted, imagining it to fire a laser projectile of sorts, and ruined their little rice cake picnic. I''ve never been able to shake that episode from my mind since I watched it as a kid.', 'Lovely Lantern Lights', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '55-revision-7', '', '', '2012-12-28 16:51:54', '2012-12-28 16:51:54', '', 55, 'http://localhost/skytreader.net/journal/55-revision-7', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(73, 1, '2012-12-29 13:11:49', '2012-12-29 13:11:49', '<h1>chad n.Â /tÊÃ¦d/</h1>\r\n<h2>chocolate-consuming, code-churning creature</h2>\r\nI code. I shoot. I blog about what I code and what I shoot.\r\n<h2>I''m a reader</h2>\r\nYep. Perhaps one of my earliest passions. Like most people my age, I''m a huge fan of J.K. Rowling''s Harry Potter. I''m also a huge fan of Neil Gaiman (and his epic, <i>The Sandman</i>). From Rowling and Gaiman, I picked up a whole slew of other authors to read like Lovecraft, Funke, and Lewis.\r\n\r\nThe literature course I took in college introduced me to a whole bunch of other authors. I did not appreciate everything in our reading list for that class but, among those I did, I ended up being fond of Italo Calvino and Arturo Perez-Reverte. Reading discussions about their work made me curious about other authors such as Umberto Eco and Aldous Huxley. Perez-Reverte made me check out other thrillers like Elizabeth Kostova''sÂ <em>The Historian</em> and Graham Moore''sÂ <em>The Sherlockian</em> ((If you managed to deduce that I''ve also read all the canonical Holmes stories, congrats!)).\r\n<h2>I''m a writer</h2>\r\n<h2>I''m a photodocumanitarian</h2>\r\n<h2>I''m a maker</h2>', 'Stuff I Do', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '13-autosave', '', '', '2012-12-29 13:11:49', '2012-12-29 13:11:49', '', 13, 'http://localhost/skytreader.net/journal/13-autosave', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
